# Talks Collection

This directory contains conference presentations, seminars, and invited talks.

## Front Matter Template

Each talk should include:
- title: Talk title
- date: Presentation date (YYYY-MM-DD)
- venue: Conference or institution name
- location: City, Country
- type: conference/seminar/invited/workshop
- slides_url: Link to slides (if available)
- video_url: Link to recording (if available)
- abstract: Brief summary
- tags: Keywords

## Example filename format:
YYYY-MM-DD-conference-short-title.md